  EffectDiscription_ENG: "Digivolve: 3 if name contains [Omnimon][When Digivolving]
    For each card with [Mega] in their traits in this Digimon\u2019s digivolution
    cards, delete 1 of your opponent\u2019s Digimon. Then, place 10 cards from your
